SubjectCanada - Republic of Korea ** Exchange of Letters **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, or to delegate authority to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the EXCHANGE OF LETTERS between the Government of Canada and the Government of the REPUBLIC OF KOREA constituting an Agreement to amend the FREE TRADE AGREEMENT between Canada and the REPUBLIC OF KOREA, done at Ottawa on 22 September 2014.
